window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>If you have an adventurous palate, join Vikram Doctor as he indulges in his appetite for the stories of food. Taste the origins, legends and practical magic of ingredients and recipes that range from the everyday to the extraordinary.</p> <p>Through ancestral kitchens, gourmet restaurants, exotic vegetable farms, modern agriculturists, heirloom aficionadosâ€¦ One of India's most respected food writers has been there, eaten that and knows that there is no love more sincere than the love of food.</p>"; 
